name: Thousand Dry Leaves
description:
Located on an isolated island, the "Ninforia Extractus" tree is dry all year round. However, every 20th of December, this tree generates a thousand identical dry leaves.
Legend has it that one of these leaves has the power to revive a person.
That said, it can be tempting to harvest all the leaves, but remember: You die if you touch the wrong leaf, and it also randomly spawns a new leaf.
